<h2>Some basics</h2>
<h3>Floats and integers</h3>
<p>
    Integers are given by default, to get a float we have to give at least one number after the decimal in one of the elements of the operation to get back a float.
</p>
<pre class="brush: python">
    >>> 3/2
    1
    >>> 3.0/2
    1.5
    >>> 
</pre>



